            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='12'>Normalized reporting intensity.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </title>
        <caption>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='22'>Represents the total number of reported bullying and harassment allegations across the five primary CRDC categories (Sex, Race, Sexual Orientation, Disability, and Religion). This metric reflects reported incidents, not verified individual cases. </run>
          </formatted-text>
        </caption>
      </layout-options>
      <table>
