    <worksheet name='Category Breakdown'>
      <layout-options>
        <title>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='20'>Reported Bullying Allegations by Protected Category</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='12'>Comparison of reported bullying allegations across the five federally protected categories collected in the CRDC 2021–2022 dataset.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </title>
        <caption>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Light' fontsize='12'>📄 Category Breakdown</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Light' fontsize='12'>Purpose</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Light' fontsize='12'>Compares reported bullying allegations across the five protected categories in the CRDC dataset.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Light' fontsize='12'>Methodology</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Light' fontsize='12'>The vw_category_summary SQL view aggregates school-level allegation counts by category. The Reporting Level groups categories by total allegation volume to make the chart easier to interpret.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Light' fontsize='12'>Key Insight</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Light' fontsize='12'>Sex- and race-based allegations account for the highest reported totals nationally. These values reflect reporting volume and should be interpreted alongside local context and reporting practices.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </caption>
      </layout-options>
      <table>
        <view>
          <datasources>
            <datasource caption='vw_category_summary (s_yoldaserdem.vw_category_summary) (nf_da_onl_09032026)' name='federated.1yugb3x0j9iwxa19y2sp81daxtfs' />
          </datasources>
          <datasource-dependencies datasource='federated.1yugb3x0j9iwxa19y2sp81daxtfs'>
