    <worksheet name='State Priority Action Matrix'>
      <layout-options>
        <title>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='20'>State Priority Action Matrix</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='12'>Identify each state’s highest-priority harassment issues and group states by common intervention needs.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </title>
        <caption>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Light' fontsize='10'>📌 Purpose</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Light' fontsize='10'>Summarizes the three most frequently reported harassment categories in each U.S. state and links them to suggested prevention priorities, enabling faster identification of common intervention needs.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Light' fontsize='10'>📖 How to Read</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Light' fontsize='10'>Each state displays its three highest-ranked harassment categories.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Light' fontsize='10'>🥇 Primary Issue = highest number of reported incidents.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Light' fontsize='10'>🥈 Secondary Issue = second highest.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Light' fontsize='10'>🥉 Third Issue = third highest.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Light' fontsize='10'>Each recommendation summarizes an evidence-based prevention focus for that harassment category.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Light' fontsize='10'>Use the </run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Light' fontsize='10'>Priority Level</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Light' fontsize='10'> filter to focus on states requiring the greatest attention.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Light' fontsize='10'>Use the </run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Light' fontsize='10'>Harassment Category</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Light' fontsize='10'> filter to identify states facing similar challenges that may benefit from shared interventions. </run>
          </formatted-text>
        </caption>
      </layout-options>
      <table>
        <view>
          <datasources>
            <datasource caption='vw_state_action_matrix (s_yoldaserdem.vw_state_action_matrix) (nf_da_onl_09032026)' name='federated.0d63tjb1wtvjb11dvlsy007h5k34' />
            <datasource name='Parameters' />
          </datasources>
          <datasource-dependencies datasource='Parameters'>
            <column caption='📊 State Ranking' datatype='string' name='[Parameter 1]' param-domain-type='list' role='measure' type='nominal' value='&quot;Highest Total Impact&quot;'>
              <calculation class='tableau' formula='&quot;Highest Total Impact&quot;' />
            </column>
          </datasource-dependencies>
          <datasource-dependencies datasource='federated.0d63tjb1wtvjb11dvlsy007h5k34'>
            <column caption='State Ranking Sort' datatype='real' name='[Calculation_5024308562800641]' role='measure' type='quantitative'>
              <calculation class='tableau' formula='IF [Parameters].[Parameter 1] = &quot;Highest Reporting Rate&quot; THEN&#10;    SUM([normalized_reporting_rate])&#10;ELSE&#10;    SUM([total_main_allegations])&#10;END' />
            </column>
